Cathy and Barb,

>

Thomasville sounds familiar, but I'm not sure where that is at in conjunction with
us--between Atlanta and Macon.� Henry county is where we are at, but we do
activities in Conyers, Jackson, Stockbridge, McDonough and Locust Grove.

> I am in Thomasville.
> Barb
